      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Pet Thing</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Things hasn't been easy lately </l>
          <l>All this talk of she loves me – well she don't </l>
          <l>But I gave up before, now I know what you're going to say. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>If you say: </l>
          <l>You're too nice to be me lover </l>
          <l>I just love you sweetie as a brother </l>
          <l>A pet, Well, I think I'll call my mother </l>
          <l>Tell her "would my sister stop bothering me" </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>You know this is what I am darling </l>
          <l>I'm cute as a puppy, I won't bite </l>
          <l>So I'm sure that you'll take advantage, </l>
          <l>you're not really my friend. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>If you say… </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>The conclusion of all this bullshit </l>
          <l>That I have to say "fuck off" for you all </l>
          <l>But you know my friend, somewhere I'll find </l>
          <l>someone fucked up like me. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>If you say…</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
